text: LA-13 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by the Former Prime Minister of Azad Kashmir Attique Ahmed Khan of Muslim Conference. It covers the area of Dhirkot Tehsil in Bagh District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016.
